<div class="banner">
  <h1>Sunshine Heroes Donation Update</h1>
</div>
<p>
  Dear <%= @donor.name %>, you have agreed to donate the following items:
</p>
<ul>
<% @donor.message.split(",").each do |i| %>
  <% if i == " " %>
    <% next %>
  <% end %>
  <li><%= i.html_safe %></li>
<% end %>
</ul>
<p>
  Deliver the following items to 3585 N University Ave #300, Provo, UT 84604 on Saturday December 16th. Thank you for your generous contribution.
  If you have any issues or concern feel free to contact us at this number 801-377-1423.
</p>
